name: Back2ThePresent
description:
You face your greatest enemy yet! But a friendly time-dude tells you that you are not synced with the present, the present where you actually win this fight! Travel back in time and sync up with the version of you that will actually prevail!

Try to match your HP and Weapon with the present you, on the timeline to victory! You get a small health boost for picking up weapons but don't get swarmed!
